    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You move to a new Town...</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>• A Combination of Life Sim Adventure, RPG and Management</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build up an old Hotel to bring joy to your future guest´s and bring back it´s past success. On your Break you can explore Odd Town, an modern town filled with residents to meet, story´s to experience and secret´s to uncover.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140470/extras/0ba8a753517e02450110bbb9c0396839.poster.avif?t=1769116211\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140470/extras/0ba8a753517e02450110bbb9c0396839.webm?t=1769116211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140470/extras/0ba8a753517e02450110bbb9c0396839.mp4?t=1769116211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>• Collecting, Customization and Management Gameplay</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect new furniture and combine them to customize and improve the hotel guest room´s. Meet your guest´s expectations to earn money or try to gain happy point´s by starting your day with a vacuum cleaner to keep your hotel nice and tidy. Use your earning´s later to upgrade your hotel and tools.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140470/extras/5b72d6915c0673ed00c26a3e063d77d4.poster.avif?t=1769116211\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140470/extras/5b72d6915c0673ed00c26a3e063d77d4.webm?t=1769116211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140470/extras/5b72d6915c0673ed00c26a3e063d77d4.mp4?t=1769116211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>• Live your Life and meet Characters with unique Story´s</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet and befriend Odd Town´s resident´s, each one with their own handcrafted story and questline. Make little presents or help them in their daily life to get closer and learn more about them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140470/extras/d247f837481b7a56063daf9969ae0851.poster.avif?t=1769116211\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140470/extras/d247f837481b7a56063daf9969ae0851.webm?t=1769116211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140470/extras/d247f837481b7a56063daf9969ae0851.mp4?t=1769116211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>• Get distracted by the many activities in Odd Town</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Next to building up your hotel you can easily get distracted by Odd Towns many activities like sidequest´s, the arcade, bug hunting, hotel gardening and much more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140470/extras/af3a3810c3310335d11e8d96b31d1b95.avif?t=1769116211\" width=495 height=192 /></span></p>",
